text: an enchanted pond deep in a hidden forest
a big old brown shingle house on Woolsey Street in Berkeley , California
the tree house that we built in the backyard
The kitchen in our mothers house
Each of the houses on the street
a green hillside overlooking the bay
the place where they pledged their love to each other so many years ago
